g, ...updates, id, updatedAt: Date.now() }`.\n5. **OrderService cancelOrder** — the `order.items` is undefined because the `update()` bug destroys the original order data. This is a cascading failure from bug 4.\n6. **Refund 30-day boundary** (`src/orders/service.ts:99`): `daysSinceCreation >= REFUND_WINDOW_DAYS` should be `>` (strictly greater than) to allow refund on exactly day 30.\n\nLet me fix all bugs now."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6404,"cache_read_input_tokens":30256,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6404},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e0442ebf-d1e4-4f99-a390-c9a537360b43","uuid":"6267006c-b978-4b43-a6a6-00559f3760c3"}
